OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779264378
OL,3,CZookeepers step in to hand-rear
OL,4,Cnewborn aardvark 'Womble'
OL,6,FZookeepers at Chester Zoo have stepped
OL,7,Fin to help raise a rare newborn
OL,8,Faardvark, bottle-feeding the tiny
OL,9,Farrival warm milk every few hours to
OL,10,Fhelp it grow.
OL,12,FThe calf is only the second aardvark
OL,13,Fever born at the zoo in its 94-year
OL,14,Fhistory, making it a highly
OL,15,Fsignificant arrival.
OL,17,FWhile the youngster was born healthy,
OL,18,Fits mother, Oni, was not producing
OL,19,Fenough milk to fully support her new
OL,20,Foffspring.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
