PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779264378
OL,3,CZookeepers step in to hand-rear
OL,4,Cnewborn aardvark 'Womble'
OL,6,FAardvarks are naturally nocturnal
OL,7,Fanimals so keepers had to provide
OL,8,Fsupplementary feeds throughout the
OL,9,Fnight for several weeks while Oni
OL,10,Fheaded off to forage for food.
OL,12,FStaff have nicknamed the calf 'Womble'
OL,13,F- after the creatures from the
OL,14,Fchildren's novels and popular TV show
OL,15,F- because of long snout, wrinkly
OL,16,Fhairless skin, and enormous claws. The
OL,17,Fanimal's sex is still unknown.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
