OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779264378
OL,3,CZookeepers step in to hand-rear
OL,4,Cnewborn aardvark 'Womble'
OL,6,FZookeeper Sophie Tyson, who bottle-fed
OL,7,Fthe calf every few hours throughout
OL,8,Fthe night, praised the youngster's
OL,9,Fprogress.
OL,11,FShe said: "For the first few weeks, we
OL,12,Fplaced the youngster into a cosy
OL,13,Fincubator each evening and it was
OL,14,Fbottle-fed warm milk every few hours
OL,15,Fthroughout the night before being
OL,16,Fcarefully reunited back with mum each
OL,17,Fmorning.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779264378
OL,3,CZookeepers step in to hand-rear
OL,4,Cnewborn aardvark 'Womble'
OL,6,F"Womble has gone from strength to
OL,7,Fstrength and is doing brilliantly, so
OL,8,Fnow lives full-time back with mum Oni
OL,9,F- and it's wonderful to see them
OL,10,Fsnuggled up side-by-side together."
OL,12,FWomble's birth is incredibly important
OL,13,Ffor international conservation efforts.
OL,15,FThere are currently only 68 aardvarks
OL,16,Fin European zoos and just 114
OL,17,Fworldwide, making Chester Zoo one of
OL,18,Fonly a few organisations caring for
OL,19,Fthe species.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
