OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779264378
OL,3,CZookeepers step in to hand-rear
OL,4,Cnewborn aardvark 'Womble'
OL,6,FIn the wild, aardvarks are native to
OL,7,Fsub-Saharan Africa, where they face
OL,8,Fserious survival threats including
OL,9,Fhabitat loss caused by rapid
OL,10,Fagricultural development and hunting.
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
